sections.text: Terms, defined.For purposes of the Employee Classification Act:(1) Commissioner means the Commissioner of Labor;(2) Construction has the same meaning as in section 48-2103;(3) Contractor means an individual, partnership, limited liability company, corporation, or other business entity engaged in a delivery service or a construction contractor business, as contractor is defined in section 48-2103, and includes any subcontractor performing services for a contractor;(4) Delivery service means the transport and delivery of goods, products, supplies, or raw materials upon the highways of this state;(5) Department means the Department of Labor; and(6) Performing services means the performance of construction labor or delivery services for remuneration.SourceLaws 2010, LB563, ยง 2.
